	width 12cm

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout

\series bold
MultiGWAS flowchart has three steps: adjustment, multi analysis, and integration.

\series default
 The first step deals with input data management, reading the configuration
 file, 
\color blue
reading and preprocessing the input genomic data
\color inherit
 (genotype and phenotype).
 The second step deals with GWAS analysis, configuring and running the four
 packages in parallel.
 And the third step deals with summarizing and reporting results using different
 tabular and graphical visualizations.
