\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout

\series bold
Shared SNPs Views.

\series default
 Tabular and graphical views of SNP associations identified by one or more
 GWAS packages (shared SNPs).
 SNPs identified by all packages are marker with red background in all figures.
 
\series bold
(a)
\series default
 Table with details of the N=8 best-ranked SNPs from each GWAS package.
 Each row corresponds to a single SNP.
 
\series bold
(b)
\series default
 Venn diagram of the best-ranked SNPs.
 SNPs identified by all packages are in the central intersection.
 Other shared SNPs are in both upper central and lower central intersections.
 
\series bold
(c)
